---- About ----

nimrod-imghdr is a Nimrod module for determining the type of an image from a given file, filename, or sequence of bytes. It can detect the PNG, JPEG, GIF, TIFF, SGI, PBM, PGM, PPM, BMP, XMB, and Sun raster formats. nimrod-imghdr is a port of Python's imghdr module.

See the documentation.html file for usage and more info.

